IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. RECURSIVE-TESTS.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-ASSERT-TOTAL    PIC 9(03) VALUE 0.
01 WS-ASSERT-PASSED   PIC 9(03) VALUE 0.
01 WS-ASSERT-FAILED   PIC 9(03) VALUE 0.
01 WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED PIC S9(9).
01 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL   PIC S9(9).
01 WS-ASSERT-NAME     PIC X(40).
01 WS-P1              PIC S9(9).
01 WS-P2              PIC S9(9).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN.
    DISPLAY "--- RECURSIVE tests ---"
    DISPLAY " "

*> ======== sum_rec ========
    MOVE 0 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 0 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "sum_rec(0)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "SUM-REC" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 3 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 6 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "sum_rec(3)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "SUM-REC" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

*> ======== factorial_rec ========
    MOVE 0 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 1 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "factorial_rec(0)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "FACTORIAL-REC" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 4 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 24 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "factorial_rec(4)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "FACTORIAL-REC" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

*> ======== fibonacci_rec ========
    MOVE 0 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 0 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "fibonacci_rec(0)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "FIBONACCI-REC" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 1 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 1 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "fibonacci_rec(1)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "FIBONACCI-REC" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 6 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 8 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "fibonacci_rec(6)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "FIBONACCI-REC" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

*> ======== gcd_rec ========
    MOVE 12 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 8 TO WS-P2
    MOVE 4 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "gcd_rec(12, 8)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "GCD-REC" USING WS-P1 WS-P2 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 7 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 5 TO WS-P2
    MOVE 1 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "gcd_rec(7, 5)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "GCD-REC" USING WS-P1 WS-P2 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

*> ======== lcm_rec ========
    MOVE 4 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 6 TO WS-P2
    MOVE 12 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "lcm_rec(4, 6)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "LCM-REC" USING WS-P1 WS-P2 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 6 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 8 TO WS-P2
    MOVE 24 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "lcm_rec(6, 8)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "LCM-REC" USING WS-P1 WS-P2 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    PERFORM ASSERT-REPORT
    GOBACK.

COPY ASSERTS.

END PROGRAM RECURSIVE-TESTS.
